'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun damu da yin kama da 'yan tsana
Wasu 'yan majalisar Wales sun yi fushi da shawarar da aka yi na maye gurbin sunayensu da MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament, Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan shawarar ta fito ne daga wani shiri na canja sunan majalisa, wadda za ta zama majalisar dokokin Wales.
A fagen siyasa, wasu 'yan majalisar sun yi imanin cewa za a iya yi wa wannan ba'a.
Wani dan takarar na Labour ya bayyana cewa kungiyar ta na damuwa da cewa kalmar  tana da alaƙa da Twp da Pwp .
Ga masu karatu da ba 'yan Wales ba: a yaren Welsh, twp yana nufin wawa, kuma pwp yana nufin ƙazanta.
Wani mai goyon bayansa ya ce, 'Plaid Cymru' (Party of Wales) ba ta gamsu da shi ba kuma ta gabatar da wasu shawarwari.
An ce jam'iyyar ta Conservative ta kasance mai bude ido ga sauya sunanta, amma ta lura cewa tsakanin MWP da Muppet (wanda ake kira 'yar tsana'), akwai nisa.
A wannan yanayin, a yaren Wales, ana furta haruffa w kamar u a yaren Turanci na yankin Yorkshire.
Hukumar Majalisar, wadda ke shirya dokokin da za su sa a canja sunayen, ta ce a karshe za a yanke shawara game da sunayen 'yan majalisar.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2007 ta ba da ikon canja sunan majalisa ta Wales.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon wani taro na jama'a game da shawarar da aka yi na nada Majalisar a matsayin majalisar dokokin Wales, wanda kuma aka yi wa goyon baya sosai.
A batun sunan 'yan majalisar, Hukumar tana goyon bayan 'yan majalisar Wales (ko WMP); duk da haka, yawancin mutanen Wales sun fi son MWP.
Da alama 'yan majalisar suna ba da wasu shawarwari, amma ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya zai iya zama babban abin damuwa ga Elin Jones, shugaban majalisar, wanda za a gabatar da wani doka game da canja sunan a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
Dokokin gyare-gyare sun haɗa da wasu canje-canje ga yadda majalisar take aiki, musamman dokokin da suka shafi ware 'yan'uwa da kuma tsarin kwamitocin.
