Indonesia: Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami Sun Kashe Daruruwan Mutane, Kuma Ana Ci Gaba da Rashin Amfani
A ranar Asabar, hukumomi sun ce akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu, da yawa daga cikinsu an kashe su ne da raƙuman ruwa masu yawa da suka rushe a rairayin bakin teku yayin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka afkawa tsibirin Celebes na Indonesia.
A ranar Jumma'a, daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin a bakin teku a Palu, sa'ad da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi na mita shida suka mamaye bakin teku da yamma, suka kashe mutane da yawa kuma suka halaka duk abin da suke tafiya.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfinsa 7.5 ta faru kafin tsunami.
 Lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta taso a jiya, kowa yana bakin rairayin bakin teku. Mutane ba su gudu ba nan da nan, sun kashe rayukansu , in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, kakakin Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Kasa (BNPB), a wani taron manema labarai a Jakarta.
 Tsunami bai faru shi kaɗai ba. Ya jawo motoci, katako, gidaje, ya ɗauki komai tare da shi , in ji Nugroho, yana mai cewa tsunami ya motsa cikin teku a cikin saurin kilomita 800 a kowace awa kafin ya buga gabar teku.
