Bayan watanni shida da aka kammala da wannan shari'ar, Kotun Duniya ta yanke shawara, kuma hakan ya nuna cewa shari'ar ba ta da wuyar warwarewa", in ji Paz Zárate, wani masanin shari'ar duniya a ƙasar Chile.
Kuma maimakon ya taimaka wa ƙasar Bolivia, wataƙila shekaru huɗu da ta yi suna da lahani.
 Gwamnatin Bolivia ta kawar da matsalar samun damar zuwa teku, in ji Zárate.
Ta ce, jawabin da Morales ya yi ya ɓata dukan mutanen Chile da suka yi nasara.
