LeBron zai fara wasa da Lakers a San Diego ranar Asabar
Yanzu haka dai, ana jiran fansar da ke jiran LeBron James ya fara buga wasan a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi a kan Nuggets na Denver, San Diego.
Amma ba mu san tsawon lokacin da zai yi ba.
Walton ya bayyana a shafin yanar gizon Lakers cewa, "Babu fiye da ɗaya ba, ba a kai 48 ba".
Dan jaridar Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa cewa, mai yiwuwa James zai buga wasan na 'yan mintoci kaɗan.
Bayan an kammala aikin, a farkon makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasan gaba, wanda ya ƙunshi wasanni shida.
A wannan lokacin na aikin, ba na bukatar wasannin da za su sa ni a shirye.
Taron Trump a West Virginia (Hanyar YouTube)
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Ana sa ran yin wasu ayyuka a wasu jihohi, musamman Tennessee da Mississippi inda shugaban kasa yake da sha'awa.
Da aka dage zaben tabbatar da matsayin da aka yi a kotun koli, Trump na neman samun goyon baya ga zaben rabin lokaci da ke zuwa kuma ya hana 'yan Republican rasa ikon da ke cikin majalisa a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai faru a West Virginia yau da dare kuma ta yaya za a kalli taron a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya bin sa a layi a ƙasa, kai tsaye a YouTube.
Trump ya yi magana game da sauraron da ake yi a wannan makon game da dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafin jima'i.
Amma, babban manufar wannan taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan jam'iyyar Republican su samu nasara a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar Reuters, shugaban Amurka ya ce a yakin neman zabensa cewa taron biyar na nufin karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin kare da fadada rinjayen da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai.
 Kula da majalisa na zama muhimmin ɓangare na shirinsa, wanda shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da yawa a farkon wannan yakin neman zabe mai wuya , wani mai magana da yawun tawagar Trump ya gaya wa Reuters, wanda ya ƙi a nada shi.
A cewar West Virginia Metro News, taron da za a yi a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling a daren yau zai iya kawo masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar, wannan ne ziyarar Trump ta biyu a cikin wata guda zuwa West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe ta da fiye da kashi 40 a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar majalisar dattijai ta West Virginia, wanda ya yi baya a zaben.
 Ba wata alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban zai zo ya sake tayar da shi a cikin kuri'u , in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: 'Yan wasan Amurka a shirye suke su yi gwagwarmaya don su ci gaba da fatan samun nasara a gasar tseren Sunday
Bayan an kammala wasan sau uku, wasan da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma zai iya nuna abin da ya rage a gasar Ryder Cup.
Yin wasan swing na yin wasan motsa jiki ra'ayi ne na wasanni da aka ƙirƙira da gaske amma 'yan wasa sun yi imani da shi sosai, kuma fiye da kowane lokaci a gasa kamar wannan.
A ina ne za su yi amfani da wannan lokacin?
"Sun ci gaba da ci gaba da maki shida, yanzu kuma hudu, don haka hakan ya ba mu wasu fuka-fuki", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake komawa ranar.
Hakika, Turai tana da fa'ida, tana da maki huɗu a gaba da kuma sauran maki 12.
Spieth ya ce 'yan Amirka suna jin cewa suna da iska a baya kuma suna da dalili mai kyau na ƙarfafa su, musamman daga Spieth da Justin Thomas da suka yi wasa tare a duk rana kuma suna iya yin alfahari da samun maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth ya nuna cewa ya yi aiki sosai daga shayi zuwa kore kuma ya kafa misali mai kyau.
Sauran muryoyin farin ciki sun kara daɗa yayin da wasan ya ci gaba, kuma wani muhimmin abu ya sa ya yi nasara a wasan na hudu yayin da Thomas da kansa suka ci nasara biyu bayan biyu.
Wannan wasan da ya sa suka ci wasan a ramin 15 na gasar, ya sa mutane suka yi ihu kamarsa, kuma sun ce yana ganin cewa tawagar Amurka tana ci gaba da yin gasa.
Spieth ya ce: "Ya kamata mu kasance da ƙuduri sosai kuma mu mai da hankali ga wasanmu.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya rage ga kowane dan wasan a yanzu.
Rukunin ramuka 18 ne da za su sa ka fita.
'Yan wasan da suka ci maki fiye da Spieth da Thomas a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, kamar yadda tarihin gasar Ryder ya nuna.
Wannan ƙaunatacciyar 'yar Turai ta ci nasara a wasanni huɗu cikin huɗu kuma ba ta da 'yancin yin kuskure.
Ba wai kawai ba su yi wasan kwaikwayo ba ne kawai a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma sun yi wasan kwaikwayo a ranar Asabar da yamma da kuma ranar Jumma'a da yamma da kuma ramin tara na ƙarshe a ranar Jumma'a da safe.
Wannan wasan, da yadda makamashi suke gudana a tsakanin su da kuma taron da ke cikin hauka suna nuna su a matsayin 'yan wasan da za su yi nasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani ɗan wasan da ya fi shahara fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari da zai iya samun nasarar Turai yayin da rana ta faɗi a Golf National.
Zai fi kyau a yi amfani da su a wurare dabam dabam a lokaci guda.
Amma yin magana game da ɗaukakar Turai ba shi da wuri.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi nasara da Sergio Garcia, gwarzon wasan kwallon kafa na safe, a lokacin da yake aiki tare da Alex Noren.
A cikin bugun farko guda tara, 'yan wasan Spain da na Sweden sun shiga rami da ba su taɓa fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimaka maka.
Ƙungiyoyi da ƙungiyoyi suna da ban sha'awa sosai don a lura da su sosai saboda yadda suke hulɗa da juna, da shawarwarin da suke bayarwa da waɗanda ba sa bayarwa, da kuma yadda dabarun zai iya juyawa a cikin ɗan lokaci.
Turai ta yi nasara a matsayin ƙungiya har zuwa yau kuma ta samu ci gaba mai yawa a ranar ƙarshe, amma wannan taron na hudu ya kuma nuna cewa Amurkawa suna da ƙarfin hali don yin gwagwarmaya, abin da wasu suka yi shakkarsa, musamman a ƙasar.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder
Turai za ta samu ci gaba mai ƙarfi a ranar ƙarshe ta gasar Ryder bayan ta ci Amurka 10-6 a wasan da aka yi a ranar Asabar.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods da ke cikin matsala, wanda ya ba su damar samun maki hudu har zuwa yanzu.
Da yake suna son su ci gaba da cin kofin da suka yi a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka shige, 'yan wasan Turai na Thomas Bjorn sun yi nasara ta hanyar buga wasan 3-1 a wasan da suka yi a safiyar yau, a gaban wani rukunin 'yan wasan Amurka da ba su da tsari.
Amurka ta nuna ƙarfi sosai a cikin 'yan wasan da suka ci nasara sau biyu, amma ba ta iya magance wannan rata ba.
Jim Furyk ya bukaci 'yan wasansa su ci maki takwas a ranar Lahadi don su ci gaba da lashe kofin.
Fleetwood ne dan wasan Turai na farko da ya samu maki hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, da ake kira  Molliwood  bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, su ne kawai biyu a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da suka samu maki hudu a wasanninsu na farko.
Bayan sun yi nasara a kan Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan da suka yi, sun yi nasara sosai a kan 'yan wasan da suka hada da dan wasan Amurka na farko Bryson Dechambeau da Woods da ya gaji da 5 da 4 da suka fi karfi.
Woods, wanda ya yi fama da rashin ƙarfi a wasannin Asabar, ya yi nasara a wasu lokutan, amma ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 da ya yi a wasanni biyu da hudu, da kuma wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya yi hutawa sosai don wasan safiya, ya yi aiki tare da Henrik Stenson a cikin wasan huɗu, ya ci nasara 2-1 a kan Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, masu lamba ɗaya da uku a duniya.
A lokacin da aka yi wasan a kudu maso yammacin birnin Paris, ba a bar Turai ba, amma a cikin yanayi mai sanyi.
Masu cin nasara uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa misali ga 'yan Amurka ta hanyar zira kwallaye biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun samu nasara mai kyau a 2-1 a kan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin kwallaye kuma sun sake doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4-3 a cikin kwallaye, waɗanda suka rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, an samu ƙungiya ta samu ta yi nisa da maki huɗu a wasan guda ɗaya, ko da yake Furyk, wanda ya riƙe kambi, ya ci gaba da yin wasan banza don ya riƙe trophy.
Bayan sun kasance na biyu na kwanaki biyu, duk da haka, ba za su iya farfadowa daga wani yaƙi da aka kai musu ranar Lahadi ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za a iya yin watsi da makamai ba a kowane hali ba.
A ranar Asabar, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ci gaba da takunkumin yana ƙarfafa rashin amincewarsa da Amurka kuma ba zai yiwu kasar ta ba da damar yin watsi da makaman nukiliya ba a irin wannan yanayin.
A taron shekara-shekara na WHO, Ri Yong Ho ya ce Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki muhimman matakan kirki a bara, kamar su dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na makami mai linzami, rushewar wurin gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma alkawarin da ta yi na hana yaduwar makamai da fasahar nukiliya.
Ya yi nadamar cewa, "Ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba".
Idan ba mu amince da Amurka ba, za mu ji tsoron tsaronmu na kasa, kuma a irin wannan yanayin, ba za mu iya zama na farko da za mu kawar da makamai ba.
Duk da yake ta sake maimaita sanannun zarge-zargen da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi game da rashin amincewar Washington da tsarin 'ƙaddamarwa' na 'yancin nukiliya wanda zai ba da lada ga Koriya ta Arewa idan ta ɗauki matakai a hankali, sanarwa ta ta tabbatar da cewa tana da muhimmanci a cikin cewa ba ta ƙi ra'ayin 'yancin nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da wata sanarwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni a Singapore a taron farko da aka yi tsakanin wani shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don kawar da makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya ta Arewa yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaro ga Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa tana neman ta kawo ƙarshen yakin Koriya (1950-1953) amma Amirka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara daina yin amfani da makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta kuma ƙi bukatar sassauta tsauraran takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka yi wa Koriya ta Arewa.
Amurka ta nace da cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta fara da kawar da makaman nukiliya kuma ta kara matsa lamba ta hanyar sanya takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilasta, har ma da adawa da "sanarwar kawo karshen yaki".
 Waɗanda suke ganin irin wannan hukunci zai iya sa mu yi rashin adalci ba su san mu ba.
Matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da tsaurara takunkumi yana sa mu ƙara rashin amincewa da juna. 
