A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai yi bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara na Global Citizen Festival, wanda ke da manyan taurari da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A bikin na bakwai na 'yan ƙasa na duniya, dubban mutane za su yi ta zuwa babban lambu na Central Park ba don su ji daɗin ayyukan da masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes suka yi ba, amma don su kuma sa mutane su san ainihin manufar bikin, wato kawar da talauci ta 2030.
Bikin 'Yan Kasa na Duniya, wanda aka fara gudanarwa a shekara ta 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ce ta kasa da kasa da ke neman kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da shi.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan ba ka son biyan tikitin VIP), masu kallo suna yin ayyuka da yawa, ko kuma ayyuka kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, kiran waya, ko kuma yin wani aiki mai amfani don wayar da kan jama'a game da yaki da talauci.
