 Da taimakon gwamnatin Birtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatoci na ƙasa, da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sa rashin cin abinci a cikin al'umma ya zama labari mai muhimmanci a tarihi , in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan shirin The Power of Nutrition a wani taro a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka yi ƙoƙari na neman fiye da 5,000 ayyuka a Birtaniya don inganta abinci mai gina jiki na iyaye mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da samun kuɗi don wani shiri, The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai amfane mata da yara miliyan 5 a cikin ayyukan abinci mai gina jiki.
