Jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar Columbia sun amince da a yi hukunci a kan sabuwar manufar Amurka ta hana mafaka ga wadanda suka tsere daga gang ko tashin hankali a gida.
A ranar Juma'a a Washington, Amurka, wakilan jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar sun gabatar da wata takarda a madadin wani mai neman mafaka da ya yi jayayya da wannan manufofin, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da kungiyar 'yancin bil'adama ta Amurka ta yi a watan Agusta ba.
Ta ce mijinta  da 'ya'yanta, 'yan gangs masu tashin hankali , sun yi mata fyade, amma hukumomin Amurka sun yanke shawarar ƙi takardar neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
