Jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da yin barazanar ta hanyar tallatawa
Wata mako bayan wani jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi na hudu da ke nuna amfanin cinikin Amurka da China a wata jaridar Amurka, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba da aka yi a kan karin kudin da China Daily ta biya a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa  bayan ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da kasar Sin ta musanta.
A zargin Beijing da yin tsalle-tsalle a zaben Amurka, Trump ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka fada wa Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne a yakin neman zabe da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba a kasar Sin.
Duk da yake gwamnatocin ƙasashen waje suna yin tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a yanzu suna cikin rikici na cinikayya da ke ƙara jawo musu haraji a kan shigo da kayayyaki.
A farkon yakin cinikayya, takunkumin haraji na kasar Sin na nufin ya shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohi kamar Iowa da suka goyi bayan Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na kasar Sin da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta yi wa ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kuma kamfanonin Amurka lahani.
Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wani labarin da aka wallafa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi cewa, kasar Sin tana ƙara yawan tsoratar da ta wajen wallafa labaran da ke cikin jaridarmu ta 'yanci.
 A wajen yada labaransa, gwamnatin Sin ta yi amfani da al'adar Amirka ta 'yancin yin magana da kuma 'yancin yada labarai ta wajen saka tallace-tallace da ake biya a cikin Des Moines Register , in ji Branstad.
 Amma a ofishin buga labarai na Beijing, za ka ga ƙarancin muryoyin masu zanga-zangar kuma ba za ka ga ainihin yadda ra'ayoyin da ke tsakanin Sin za su iya nunawa game da matsalar tattalin arzikin Sin ba, domin kafofin watsa labarai suna bin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin , in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa, wata babbar jarida a kasar Sin ta guji wallafa labarinta, ba tare da bayyana wane jarida ba.
Masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa 'yan Republican suna ware 'yan mata daga zaben rabin lokaci saboda matsalar Kavanaugh
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican ke kare Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli a kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i, masu bincike sun yi gargadin cewa za a iya samun mummunan martani, musamman ga mata, a lokacin zaben rabin lokaci na gaba.
A halin yanzu, akwai wasu abubuwa da suka faru da suka sa 'yan Republican da yawa suka nuna a fili cewa suna son a yi zabe.
A wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba a The Hill, Grant Reeher, wani farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a makarantar Maxwell a jami'ar Syracuse ya ce ba za a iya komawa baya ba.
Reeher ya kara da cewa yana shakkar cewa kokarin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Ariz.) ya yi na neman binciken FBI zai iya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin kasa na kungiyar MoveOn, ta ce, 'mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru a jiya ba; ba za su manta da shi ba gobe, ba a watan Nuwamba ba,' in ji ta a ranar 28 ga Satumba, a cewar jaridar Washington.
A safiyar Juma'a, Mic ta ruwaito, masu zanga-zangar sun rera waƙa a cikin majalisar dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zaɓi su ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford.
 Za a yi amfani da himma da kuma motsawar dimokiradiyya sosai , in ji Stu Rothenberg, mai nazarin siyasa marar bangare.
Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya yi girma, gaskiya ne.
Amma wannan zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman a cikin 'yan mata masu jefa kuri'a na karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29 waɗanda, ko da yake ba sa son shugaban kasa, sau da yawa ba sa jefa kuri'a. 
Kafin Ford ya ba da cikakken bayani game da zargin cin zarafin da ake yi wa dan takarar Kotun Koli, masu bincike sun yi imanin cewa idan 'yan Republican suka yi hakan, za su yi fushi sosai.
A cewar NBC News, tsohon shugaban kwamitin jam'iyyar Republican, Michael Steele, ya ce a farkon makon da ya gabata cewa, wannan ya zama rikice-rikice ga jam'iyyar GOP.
 Ba wai kawai game da zaɓen kwamitin ko zaɓen ƙarshe ba ne, ko kuma zaɓen Kavanaugh, amma kuma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da yanayin da kuma yadda suka bi da shi , Guy Cecil, darektan Ƙungiyar Fifiko ta Amurka, wata ƙungiya da ke taimaka wa 'yan Democrat da aka zaɓa, ya gaya wa jaridar TV.
Amma, bayan shaidar da Ford da Kavanaugh suka bayar, Amirkawa sun nuna cewa ba su yarda da abin da waɗannan jam'iyyun biyu suka faɗa ba, kuma yawancin mutane sun amince da su.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na mutanen da aka bincika sun gaskata da shaidar Ford ko kuma sun yi imani da ita, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun gaskata da Kavanaugh ko kuma sun yi imani da shi.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun gaskata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da ya ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka ce haka game da Ford.
A cewar jaridar The Guardian, FBI na binciken zargin da Ford da kuma akalla wata mai tuhuma, Deborah Ramirez suka yi bayan Sanata Flake ta matsa musu.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a lokacin da yake cikin shaye-shaye yana da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ya ce lokacin da suke Yale a shekarun 1980, 'yan takarar Kotun Koli sun nuna masa jima'i a wani biki.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ya yi niyyar kaddamar da sabuwar intanet don kalubalanci Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya kaddamar da sabuwar kamfani da ke neman yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da ya fi dacewa da fasahar zamani, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke amfani da dandamali na Berners-Lee na Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda aka ba da izinin samun damar yin amfani da irin wannan bayanin.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ta ba'a cewa Inrupt yana nufin  mamaye duniya .
Ya ce game da ƙaddamar da jirgin, dole ne mu yi hakan yanzu.
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi ko DPL.
Wannan na iya ƙunsar jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa da kuma wasu kayan aiki na mutum da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify suna samuwa a lokaci guda a cikin mai bincike guda.
Wani abu na musamman da ke shagon yanar gizo na bayanan sirri shi ne cewa mai amfani ne ya yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun dama ga wane irin bayani.
Kamfanin yana kiran wannan "hakkin mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar Shugaba John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce kamfanin ya ba da albarkatu, hanyoyin da kuma ƙwarewar da suka dace don yin Solid ya zama mai sauƙi ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, dandalin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da ke aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu ba da kyauta na coders.
Daga wannan makon, masu ci gaba da fasaha a duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke samuwa a shafin yanar gizon dInrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba don su san ko za su yi canji mai yawa inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya zama mummunan aiki a cikin wani lokaci.
Ba mu nemi izinin su ba.
A wata kasida da ta fito a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa manufa ta [dInrupt] ita ce samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu don kare mutuncin da kuma ingancin sabon yanar gizo da aka gina akan Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya yi aiki a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts don ya canja Intanet ta wajen kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance babbar murya a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na cibiyar sadarwa.
Ko da yake ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma ya kasance darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation da Open Data Institute.
 Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabon zamani na yanar gizo , Berners-Lee ya kara da cewa.
Bernard Vann: Wani limamin yaƙin duniya na farko da aka saka da Gicciye na Victoria
