Mickelson ya yi rauni a kan benci na gasar Ryder a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47 a ranar Lahadi, amma zai yi gyara domin kada ya zama wani abin takaici.
Mickelson, wanda ya shiga gasar ta shekara biyu a karo na 12, wanda ya zama rikodin, ya kasance a hannun Kyaftin Jim Furyk daga kwallaye da kwallaye a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda ya kasance a yawancin lokaci a Amurka, mai nasara biyar ya raba ranarsa tsakanin aikinsa na tallafawa da kuma daidaita wasan sa a kan teburin domin ya magance matsalolinsa.
A shekara ta 48, bai dace da wasan golf na kasa ba, inda dogon raunin ya yi wa waɗanda suka rasa nasara horo.
Kuma kamar dai ba a yi wa filin wasa tsoro ba, Mickelson a wasan tara na ranar Lahadi ya yi wa Francesco Molinari, wanda ya lashe gasar cin kofin Birtaniya, wanda ya yi aiki tare da Tommy Fleetwood a wannan makon don ya lashe wasanni huɗu.
Idan 'yan wasan Amurka da suka ci nasara a farkon wasannin 12 na wasan kwaikwayo na farko suka fara wasa da kyau, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai matukar muhimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa ya amince da mutumin, amma ba shi da abin da zai faɗa.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci cewa yana da aiki sosai a yau, ya buge ni a baya, ya rungume ni, ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe.
 Yana da cikakken tabbaci a kansa.
Shi ne babban zakara kuma ya kara abubuwa da yawa ga waɗannan kungiyoyin a baya, kamar yadda ya yi a wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban gan shi yana wasa biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin cewa ba za mu yi hakan ba, amma hakan ne ya faru kuma mun ga cewa hakan ne ya kamata mu yi.
Yana son ya kasance a can, kamar kowa. 
A ranar Lahadi Mickelson zai karya rikodin Nick Faldo na yawan wasan da aka buga a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan zai iya kawo ƙarshen wani wasan Ryder Cup da bai taɓa kai matsayin da ya kafa ba.
Mickelson yana da nasara 18, 20 da kuma 7 da rabi, ko da yake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ta kawo abubuwa masu kyau ga tawagar.
Yana da ban dariya, mai ba'a, mai ruhaniya, yana son yin ba'a da mutane, kuma yana da kyau sosai a cikin dakin ƙungiyar, in ji shi.
 Na yi tunanin 'yan wasan matasa sun ji daɗin yin wasa da shi a wannan makon, wanda ya kasance mai ban sha'awa.
Ba wasa kawai yake yi ba.
Shugaban kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai Thomas Bjorn ya san cewa za a iya kawar da ci gaban da ake samu a gasar
Thomas Bjorn, wanda yake shugaban Turai, ya san cewa yin tsalle-tsalle kafin wasan Ryder Cup na ƙarshe zai iya zama aiki mai wuya.
Danish din ya buga wasansa na farko a 1997 a Valderrama, inda wani rukuni da ya jagoranci Seve Ballesteros ya ci gaba da ci gaba da Amurkawa da maki biyar, amma a ƙarshe ya tashi zuwa saman jerin tare da mafi ƙarancin bambanci a kan layin ƙarshe, ya ci 141⁄2-131⁄2.
 Kuna tuna cewa mun ci gaba da samun nasara a Valderrama; muna da babban ci gaba a Brookline, inda muka gaza, da kuma a Valderrama, inda muka ci nasara, amma daidai ne  in ji Bjorn, bayan kallon 2018 Ranking ya ci nasara 5-3 a ranar Jumma'a da jiya a Golf National don kaiwa 10-6.
