Fadar White House ta sanar da cewa taron Trump da Rosenstein na iya jinkirta
A cewar sanarwar da Fadar White House ta yi a ranar Lahadi, za a iya dage taron da ke da manyan matsaloli tsakanin Donald Trump da Mataimakin Babban Shari'a Rod Rosenstein na mako guda yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmayar neman takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin Robert Mueller, mai ba da shawara na musamman da ke bincika tsoma baki na Rasha a zaben, da alaƙar da ke tsakanin abokan aikin Trump da Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban yin adalci.
Tambayar ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauya ko a'a, kuma hakan zai sa 'yancin Mueller ya kasance cikin haɗari, ta yi ta ba da labari ga Washington na tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya yi magana game da saka makirufo don yin rikodin tattaunawar da ya yi da Trump da kuma yiwuwar kawar da shugaban kasar ta hanyar Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta waɗannan kalaman.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya bayyana kansa a fadar White House, a lokacin da yake gab da barin aiki.
A maimakon haka, an sanar da cewa za a gana da Trump a ranar Alhamis a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya.
Trump ya ce zai fi son kada ya sallami Mista Rosenstein, amma an dage taron ne don kauce wa rikici da kotun shari'a ta Majalisar Dattawa da ta halarci shari'ar Kavanaugh da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, ɗaya daga cikin matan da suka zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya bukaci FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan korafin da aka yi game da Kavanaugh, wanda ya kara jinkirta zaben Majalisar Dattawa.
A ranar Lahadi, ma'aikaciyar Trump ta Sarah Sanders ta bayyana a gidan talabijin na Fox News.
Da aka tambaye ta game da taron da ta yi da Rosenstein, ta ce: 'Ba a ba da kwanan wata ba, za a iya yin hakan a wannan makon, zan iya ganin ko za a sake jinkirta shi na mako guda saboda duk sauran abubuwan da ke faruwa a Kotun Koli.
Amma za mu ga kuma ina son in sanar da manema labarai.
Wasu 'yan jarida sun yi jayayya da wannan ikirarin: tun ranar 10 ga Satumba, Sanders bai yi taron manema labarai a fadar White House ba.
Mai gabatar da taron Chris Wallace ya tambaye ni dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ta amsa cewa rashin taron ba don ƙiyayya da 'yan jarida ba ne a talabijin, ko da yake ta ce: "Ba ni da wani abu game da yadda suka yi wa gidan wasan kwaikwayo mamaki".
Bayan haka, ta nuna cewa za a kara samun lamba tsakanin Trump da manema labarai.
Ba tare da ta ambata wata hujja ba, ta kara da cewa shugaban kasa yana halartar taro da amsoshi fiye da kowane shugaban kasa kafin shi: Mun duba alkaluman.
Sanders ya ce za a riƙa yin taron manema labarai a kowane lokaci, amma idan 'yan jarida sun samu damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, hakan zai fi kyau fiye da yin magana da ni.
Muna ƙoƙarin yin hakan a kai a kai, kamar yadda kuka gani a cikin 'yan makonnin nan, kuma wannan zai maye gurbin taron manema labarai inda za ku iya magana da shugaban Amurka.
A kai a kai, Trump yana amsa tambayoyi a lokacin da yake barin fadar White House ko kuma lokacin da yake halartar taron jama'a ko kuma taron manema labarai da manyan mutane.
Ba a yawan yin jawabi a kai a kai a taron manema labarai a wurin.
A wannan makon, a birnin New York, shugaban ya nuna dalilin da ya sa, ta wajen yin wani abu mai ban mamaki a gaban 'yan jarida.
A kan fargaba game da Brexit, Sakataren Lafiya ta rubuta wa ma'aikatan EU a NHS Scotland
Sakataren kiwon lafiya ta rubuta wa jami'an EU da ke aiki a NHS na Scotland don nuna godiya ga ƙasar kuma ta yi fatan za su ci gaba da aiki bayan Brexit.
'Yar majalisa ta Scotland, Jeane Freeman, ta aika da wata wasiƙa a cikin kasa da watanni shida kafin Birtaniya ta fice daga EU.
Gwamnatin Scotland ta riga ta yi alkawarin biyan kudin neman matsayin 'yan Turai da ke aiki a cikin ayyukanta na gwamnati.
Freeman ya rubuta a cikin wasiƙarsa cewa:  A lokacin rani, tattaunawar janyewa ta ci gaba tsakanin Birtaniya da EU kuma ana sa ran yanke shawara a wannan kaka.
Amma gwamnatin Birtaniya ta kuma tsaurara shirye-shiryenta idan ba a cimma matsaya ba.
