Wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ne, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda aka kiyasta yawan mazaunansa a shekara ta 2017.
A lokacin da aka yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami, birnin ya cika shekara 40 da kafuwa.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
An kiyasta yawan mutanen da ke cikin yankin regency, wani yanki na gwamnati da ke ƙarƙashin lardin, zuwa 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
