Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani babban girgizar ƙasa da ya faru a yammacin tekun Aceh a ƙasar Indonesia a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ya jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta girgiza yammacin Sumatra daga ƙarshen Maris zuwa farkon Afrilu.
