2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibirin da aka fi yawan zama a Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya afkawa gabar tekun kudu kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
A shekara ta 2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 ta girgiza birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfinsa 7.5 ta halaka tsibirin Mentawai da ke gabar Sumatra kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
