Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci hukuncin kisa mai wuya ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York sun bukaci a yi masa hukuncin kisa don Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da laifin New York da ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a yi a jihar ba tun 1953.
An ce Saipov mai shekara 30 ya yi amfani da wata babbar mota da aka haya daga gidan ajiyar kayayyaki na Home Depot don ya kai hari a kan titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya kashe wani mai hawa da kuma wani mai hawa keke a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba na shekarar da ta gabata.
Don a yi musu hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci su ba da hujja cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi musu lahani mai tsanani, a cewar sanarwar da aka yi a Kotun Kudancin New York.
Wannan zargi biyu na iya kai ga hukuncin kisa, kamar yadda takardar shari'a ta nuna.
Bayan 'yan makonni bayan wannan harin, babban kotun tarayya ya yanke hukuncin kisa a kan Saipov bisa zargin 22 da ake masa, ciki har da zargin kisa takwas da ake yi wa masu gabatar da kara na tarayya don karbar kudi, wanda a yawancin lokaci masu gabatar da kara ke amfani da shi wajen gudanar da ayyukan aikata laifuka da kuma aikata laifuka na lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci shiri da kuma tunani sosai, suna cewa hanyar da Saipov ya yi amfani da ita ta zama abin ƙyama, da zalunci da kuma lalata.
 Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lalacewa da asarar rayuka , in ji sanarwar niyya.
