Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a birnin Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 ta doke ƙungiyar Amurka da ƙimar ƙarshe daga 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Golf National kusa da Paris, Faransa.
A yanzu dai, Amurka ta yi nasara sau shida a kan Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta ci gaba da lashe kofin a lokacin da Thomas Bjorn ya ci gaba da zira kwallaye 14.5 a kan Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa farawa a cikin ruwa a ramin 16 a cikin par-3, yana mika duel ga Francesco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi nasara a duk faɗin gasar, ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka taɓa samun ci gaba 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar, wanda aka fara a shekara ta 1979.
Dan wasan Denmark Thorbjorn Olesen, wanda ya fi kowacce rawa a Turai, ya yi wa Jordan Spieth na Amirka baya da maki 5 zuwa 4.
Dustin Johnson, mai wasan golf mafi kyau a duniya, ya yi nasara da Ingila, Ian Poulter, wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder ta ƙarshe.
Wani tsohon dan wasan Spain mai suna Sergio Garcia, ya lashe kofin Turai na dukan lokaci da ya samu maki 25.5 a rayuwa.
